<p><b>Human Rights Council 
Twenty-sixth session 
</b>Agenda item 3 
<b>Promotion and protection of all human rights, civil, 
political, economic, social and cultural rights,  
including the right to development  
</b></p>
<p><b>  Report of the Special Rapporteur on the human rights of 
migrants, Mr. Fran&#231;ois Cr&#233;peau 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Addendum 
</b></p>
<p><b>Comments by the Qatari Government on the report of the Special 
Rapporteur* 
</b></p>
<p>  
</p>
<p> 
</p>
<p>*
 Reproduced in the annex as received. 
